tip.text: Ok for lunch but missing the details
International atmosphere, outstanding food, good service - representative fine dining with a causal touch
Genuine and generous portions! Love it!
Great place for dim sums and good value.
Nice local produced food. Plenty of seats inside.
Good lunch with the opportunity to try the local classics as smoked flounder and the beef toast with chanterelles. Good selection in deli corner to bring home.
Not for the picky sushi lover. Choose the classics on the meny .
Nice cake selection and even a menu for dogs
Home made  bread and soups on the menu
Good value. Fresh seafood. Friendly staff. Kids love chicken with cashew nuts . We always order clams with lemongrass, BBQ prawns with garlic and deep fried squid.
